@startuml
[*] --> Order : newly acquired
Order --> Arrival : delivered
Arrival --> Preparation : arrived
Preparation --> Operations : condition met and schedule allows
Preparation --> Maintenance : condition not met or schedule requires
Operations --> Operations : still has scheduled flights
Operations --> Maintenance : no more flights or maintenance required
Maintenance --> Preparation : checked and serviced
Order --> Retired : taken out of service
Arrival --> Retired : permanently withdrawn
Preparation --> Retired : permanently withdrawn
Operations --> Retired : permanently withdrawn
Maintenance --> Retired : permanently withdrawn
@enduml
